    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "念",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "香柳娘卖头发！卖头发！卖头发！看青丝细发，看青丝细发，根连血脉。勤梳巧理多关爱，没奈何狠心一剪，奈何狠心一剪，身与发两分开。提一束——𠮾——珠泪垂，一声声叫卖，一声声叫卖，过长街短街，我的脚儿难抬。那日婆婆吃糠而亡，不想公公昨夜又随她而去，一双尸首停放中堂，无钱埋葬，只得剪下头发卖几贯钱钞以为送终只用。想这头发是我身上之物，如何拿来叫卖？事到如今也顾不得羞惭，只得长叫一声——卖头发！这位大哥，可要买头发？这位大嫂，买了奴家的头发吧！众位爷爷奶奶，买了奴家的头发吧！想我赵五娘——不幸丧双亲，求人不可频。聊将青丝发，断送白头人！那一双无言尸骸，一双无言尸骸，谁人与遮盖？若葬了双亲，奴便死何害？（夹白）头发呀！（香柳娘）你离身去根儿何在？离身根儿何在？可知我夫君别去，他不回来，只落得发断人离，长跪在尘埃。一声卖头发，一阵哭哀哀，纵然是千丝万缕，万缕千丝，https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709021452023-10-05牵不转来奴的伯喈，奴的伯喈……",
      "text_length": 443
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "卖头发！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵五娘昏厥。张广才上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "慈悲胜念千声佛，造恶空烧万柱香。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "老汉张广才。昨日见蔡家老哥病情十分危急，使我放心不下，不免今日前去探望与他。什么东西险些绊了我一跤？啊，这不是五娘子？五娘子醒来！",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "原来是大公！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "五娘子因何跌倒在地？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "奴家离家出门，一时乏力，故而跌倒在地。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "老汉不便搀扶，就在这拄杖之上撑了起来。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "扶好了！小心了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "多谢大公！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "五娘子，你不在家中照看公公，来到这大街之上作甚？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "大公啊，公公昨夜没了！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "怎么说？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "公公昨夜没了！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "啊？啊呀老哥啊，昨日我还与你讲话，你怎么今日就没了……你手上拿的是什么东西？",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "是头发。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "要它何用？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "公婆没了，无钱埋葬，剪下头发卖几贯钱钞，以为送终之用。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "五娘子，你公公没了，就该与我商议才是。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "屡受大公周济，怎么又来启齿？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张广才"
      ],
      "text": "五娘子，这就是你的不是了！想你我两家祖居陈留，世代相好，互为邻里，亲如一家，如今你家中出了这样的大事，我岂能袖手旁观？况且你丈夫上京之日，已将家中之事托付与我，如今他父母双亡，你无钱埋葬，就将自己头发剪下，长街叫卖，这岂不伤了父母之遗体，我若不管，怎能对得起老哥老嫂，又怎能对得起远在京城的蔡伯喈？不必多言，你速速回去，我即刻差人送钱送米过来。",
      "text_length": 172
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵五娘"
      ],
      "text": "大公恩德无以为报。受奴一拜！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902145_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902145",
      "scene_id": "70902145_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
